                    <P><img class="emoticon emoticon-surprised" id="surprised" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/surprised.png" alt="Surprised" title="Surprised" /> Is it really Peter?!?!&nbsp; Mayhap it is yet another monstrous illusion that takes the form of the scariest monster yet, for Lady Jonna, which is Peter the Pizza, methinks, or perhaps it&nbsp;truly <EM>is</EM> Peter!</P><P>&nbsp;</P><P>The primary fear of mine is pretty well known.&nbsp; Or at least I believe it to be.&nbsp; Sir Talmid is quite similar to me, so it is likely he shares similar characteristics such as fears with me.</P><P>&nbsp;</P><P>&nbsp;</P><div class="lia-spoiler-container"><a class="lia-spoiler-link" href="#" rel="nofollow">Jammers</a><noscript> (Highlight to read)</noscript><div class="lia-spoiler-border"><div class="lia-spoiler-content">Spiders must be eradicated from the known universe.</div><noscript><div class="lia-spoiler-noscript-container"><div class="lia-spoiler-noscript-content">Spiders must be eradicated from the known universe.</div></div></noscript></div></div><P>&nbsp;</P><P>&nbsp;</P>
                
            
			
